San Andreas: Multiplayer Advanced Functionality Plugin

====================

Client-side game-loadable module that communicates with another TCP server (transfering data/game extensibility/etc).
High security conception & user frendly.

Based on samp-addon by BJIADOKC
https://github.com/BJIADOKC/samp-addon




====================
CLIENT
====================

WARNING:
  ALL .ASI FILES FROM GTA:SA DIRECTORY WILL BE REMOVED DUE TO SECURITY MEASURES (Excludes whitelist's ones, like audioplugin)





